@startuml seq-rf09-rf10-autenticacao
title RF09 + RF10 - Autenticacao OIDC e autorizacao RBAC

actor Comerciante
participant "Front Blazor" as Front
participant "Amazon Cognito" as Cognito
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "API .NET" as API

== Login ==
Comerciante -> Front: Acessa aplicacao
Front -> Cognito: Authorization Code + PKCE
Cognito --> Comerciante: Tela de login
Comerciante -> Cognito: Credenciais
Cognito --> Front: access_token + id_token
note right of Cognito: claims: merchant_id,\ncognito:groups, scopes

== Chamada protegida ==
Comerciante -> Front: Registrar lancamento
Front -> APIGW: POST /api/lancamentos\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}
APIGW -> Cognito: Valida assinatura JWT (JWKS)
alt Token invalido ou expirado
    APIGW --> Front: 401 Unauthorized
else Token valido
    APIGW -> API: Request + claims
    API -> API: Policy RBAC\n(merchant_operator | admin)
    alt Sem permissao
        API --> APIGW: 403 Forbidden
    else Autorizado
        API -> API: Filtra por merchantId do token
        API --> APIGW: 201 Created
    end
    APIGW --> Front: Resposta
end

note over API: Status POC: auth nao implementada

@enduml
